boilerplate for grunt project

1. Download repo from github;
2. Execut following command under this repo directory:
    npm install
3. Execut following command for using grunt:
    grunt
    grunt clean
    grunt dist-js
    grunt dist-css
    grunt test-js
    grunt dist
4. Change configuration in configBridge.json file:
/*对html中的引用的文件进行合并*/
"htmlpaths"
/*对合并后的文件进行压缩*/
"htmlpaths_min"
/*对各个目录的js文件进行合并文件*/
"jspaths"
/*对合并后的js文件进行压缩*/
"jspaths_min"
/*对各个目录中的css文件进行合并*/
"csspaths"
/*对合并后的css文件进行压缩*/
"csspaths_min"
/*将开发目录下的图片资源copy到发布目录下*/
  "imagespaths"